Package: spectrotune
Title: Spectral Pretreatment and Nested CV Modeling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("John", "Albechaalany", email = "Johnbechaalany@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Comprehensive spectral data analysis package for pretreatment, model benchmarking, and visualization. Supports regression and classification with nested cross-validation, multiple algorithms (PLSR, SVR, GLMNET, RIDGE, KRR_RBF, RF, XGB_PCA, RF_PCA, SVM, PLSDA), and advanced sampling strategies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
